55-SKY130RTL D5SK5 L3 â†’ Lab: For & For Generate (Part 3)
ğŸ”¹ Why prefer for-generate over manual structural instantiation

Scalability â†’ avoids writing hundreds of repetitive module instances manually.

Parameterization â†’ design size changes automatically with a parameter (N).

Readability & Maintainability â†’ much cleaner and less error-prone code.

Consistency â†’ guarantees identical hardware replication without copy-paste mistakes.

